  "title": "Clinic Receptionist",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Responsible for day to day operations at the clinics</li><li>Communicate and provide assistance to our patients/members</li><li>Schedule appointments and answer telephone enquiries and emails</li><li>Maintain and update client database</li><li>Management of invoice and payments at the clinics</li><li>Participate in corporate events (if required)</li><li>Ad-hoc duties assigned by the management</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess good communication skills, with a pleasant disposition</li><li>Meticulous and systematic with administrative procedures</li><li>Believe in the mission – to enable our community to live lift at its fullest</li><li>Responsible, dependable, trustworthy and punctual</li><li>Willingness to learn and grow in a demanding environment</li><li>Confident and fluent in English.</li><li>Previous experience in sales, customer service or working in clinics is preferred</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Leave and medical benefits</li><li>Healthcare benefits amongst brands under The Health Collective</li></ul><p>Applications will be considered on a rolling basis.</p>",
